## 

Dynamo

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[Frontend HTTP Server] --> B[Request Router]
    B --> C[Worker Pool]
    C --> D[vLLM Workers]
    C --> E[TensorRT-LLM Workers]
    C --> F[SGLang Workers]
    
    G[KV Cache Manager] --> H[Memory Service]
    I[Discovery Service] --> J[Service Registry]
    
    K[Event Plane] --> L[NATS/JetStream]
    M[Request Plane] --> N[TCP/NATS/HTTP]
    
    O[Monitoring] --> P[Prometheus Metrics]
    Q[Observability] --> R[Tracing]
```

### 

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Frontend
    participant Router
    participant Worker
    participant KVCache
    
    Client->>+Frontend: HTTP Request
    Frontend->>+Router: Process Request
    Router->>+KVCache: Check Cache State
    KVCache-->>-Router: Cache Info
    Router->>+Worker: Route to Best Worker
    Worker->>+KVCache: Update Cache
    KVCache-->>-Worker: Cache Updated
    Worker-->>-Router: Generation Result
    Router-->>-Frontend: Response
    Frontend-->>-Client: Final Response
```
